description:
Redmi Note 14 Pro
200MP AI cameraAll-Star Durability
Advanced imaging performance
with a 200MP AI camera
Equipped with a flagship-level 200MP main camera, powerful hardware and OIS (optical image stabilisation), the Redmi Note 14 Pro provides clearer details and purer night shots.
Xiaomi Imaging Engine
AI-boosted algorithm
Capture ultra-clear 200MP images with rich details and vibrant colors.
4× lossless zoom
Optical-level lossless zoom
With both 2× and 4× optical-grade lossless zoom, you can easily switch between different focal lengths to frame your shot without a pixel out of place.
Alluring night shots
Discover the beauty of the dark
RAW algorithms have been further refined to retain more image details and make night shots even more stunning.
AI Erase Pro
Erase unwanted clutter from your photos with AI Erase Pro. Just tap on what you want to remove and watch as it magically disappears!
Corning® Gorilla® Glass Victus® 2
Drop and scratch-resistant
The flagship-level durable glass screen delivers unparalleled strength that effortlessly withstands accidental drops.
Chat with Gemini, a truly helpful personal AI assistant from Google, to supercharge your ideas.
The new Redmi Note 14 Pro is elegantly curved for a fresh and vibrant appearance.
Eye-care display
Our built-in eye protection feature automatically adjusts the screen color temperature to match the time of day. It also helps to enhance eye comfort when using your phone in the dark, reducing visual fatigue.
The 4,094-level automatic brightness adjustment and fineness enable more comfortable light changes. Also, the display adopts 1920Hz PWM dimming and DC dimming. It can reduce flicker and alleviate eye fatigue even at low brightness.
